"        &bull; Prior birth of a high-risk infant",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"sublist2\">",
"        &bull; Antepartum hemorrhage",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"sublist2\">",
"        &bull; Premature rupture of membranes",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"sublist2\">",
"        &bull; Serious infection during pregnancy",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"sublist2\">",
"        &bull; Placental anomalies - praevia, polyhydramnios or oligohydramnios, pregnancy-induced hypertension, Group B streptococcus carrier",
