"      <tr>",
"       <td colspan=\"4\">",
"        &bull;&nbsp;If \"YES\" follow up as a potential overlap syndrome. If patient has Raynaud's phenomenon and systemic involvement in conjunction with persistent U1-RNP antibodies, the most likely diagnosis will turn out to be mixed connective tissue disease (MCTD).",
